        Note over C,EM: NREM Phase (75% of cycle)

        C->>+EM: get_consolidation_candidates(top_k=100)
        EM->>EM: priority_sort(outcome, importance, recency)
        EM-->>-C: episodes[100]

        loop SWR Replay Sequences
            C->>C: build_swr_sequence(similarity>0.5)
